Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a delivery for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you've cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no point in feeling depressed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We got word that Flange's fleet is in the Sea of Fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The galaxy current seems to be flowing that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so we might end up sailing in the same area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a chance that we'll find out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Pinion didn't do anything too stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all that matters to me is that they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing's huge! Is it pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the whole fleet on emergency alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't make any careless moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Pinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll call him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel? Is that you, Colonel Kugel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up your distress signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I was on the other side of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you contacted me, I would've come to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to keep radio silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Ledo will now return to the Kugel squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gigantic! This ain't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we retreat, Pinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat? To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We got this cannon and the Metalhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we give them a nice, warm welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Target aligned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How d'you like that? Go run to momma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a lightning bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at what you've done to my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Metalhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ledo! Ledo, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Lt. Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now return to the ranks of the Galactic Alliance of Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo! Metalhead!
