Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Guiding signal acknowledged. Commencing landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize it is a collective action to demonstrate the unity of their group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So he took command of the locals?{Xythar, check this "So" for a comma. <3 I'm gonna leave the introductory adverbial commas (the single-word ones, at least) for you, as usual.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We welcome you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,O herald of the skies, clad in a thunder giant's form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of Providence, we wish you peace and prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe those are idiosyncrasies referring to Machine Calibers and their pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Colonel Kugel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse my use of a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Kugel! I'm happy to see you alive and well and on this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A endemic disease got the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unable to leave my sterilized cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No such problems, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Having to issue orders from here is (such/quite) a nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you around will help a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say? Will you follow me once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber K6821 to Striker X3752:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I request information about the aforementioned endemic disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Striker X3752 to Chamber K6821.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Request acknowledged. Transmitting data.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We got the treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really gonna be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,5,,If things turn sour, the Metalhead—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,5,,Didn't they just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.39,Default,,0,0,5,,We're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,5,,C-Come on now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,5,,We don't know what they want either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,5,,What else could they want\N\Nbut the ancient treasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,5,,How would they know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.29,Default,,0,0,5,,You broadcast it for the whole world to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,5,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,5,,Uh... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.78,Default,,0,0,5,,I doubt you have the time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.49,Default,,0,0,5,,Don't butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.71,Default,,0,0,5,,Look around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.33,Default,,0,0,5,,Get back to your positions immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the weapon's in the hands of one of Ledo's comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was more than one visitor from the skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what could he possibly want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Urgent message!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The fleet just got hailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Flange speaking. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They demand the presence of our representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't specified a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be here for the relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm responsible for this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see to it that it gets cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no time for your delusions of grandeur. I can't trust you with diplomatic negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They demanded Pinion of the Sea of Fog as our representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were taken hostage, who'd keep this fleet together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Even if I stayed here, no one would follow me after I screwed up this badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing. Off I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait here. They said they're gonna send a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"No one would follow me after screwing up this badly."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been a loser. No one's gonna leave over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Surfing Lobster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Pinion of the Sea of Fog, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. What a surprise to see Rackage, the great queen of pirates herself, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just "Rackage" will do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do well to mind that mouth of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Times look hard. Are they eating at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak serve the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the God's Providence, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your "God" being... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a thunder giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A servant of God that supposedly hands down divine judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,While the humans of this planet do get to live in such a luxuriant environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,they must do so under the constant oppression of the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Our duty is to teach them to defend themselves and become missionaries of mankind's glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As for that, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Former humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not something that was discussed, even in the upper echelons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For those of us fighting on the front-line, it is only unnecessary information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Unnecessary, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze are driven by hunger and base instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot be called humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the strong and the weak support each other with reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They contribute in their own way to the formation of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what it means to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have brought order to this fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the average well-being of the people here has risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I request the definition of "well-being" in this context.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on the principles of the Galactic Alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"well-being" is defined as the state in which the cost-benefit performance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of the individual's contribution to the community is maximized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, well-being correlates directly with the stability of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with this definition and conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Ledo. Won't you help me change this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, no one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this then?{Xythar, consider a comma before this "then." I'd opt for it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion of the Sea of Fog, we welcome you as our distinguished guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck? It was a transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It is necessary for the technology of the humans on Earth to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a test to measure the skills of Pinion of the Sea of Fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aptitude is judged to be promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound familiar. Are you a relative of the Metalhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the pilot support system Striker X3752.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And what might you want from me, Striker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We commend you on restoring a cannon retrieved from the sea floor to operational capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it is but a temporary measure that lacks an understanding of the underlying structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I got no idea how that ancient machinery stuff works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We are willing to provide you with information on that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With your skills, repairing weaponry would only be the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Designing and manufacturing new weapons are within your capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure think highly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been deemed to be capable of handling such technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our final demand is that you display leadership as an engineer officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Officer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't no soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, can you guarantee the safety of our fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Valuable human resources are not to be expended without a rational cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Expended"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can guarantee our safety, I'm willing to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect great things from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Read this before you eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner you speak, the sooner we'll be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a stuck-up one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit still, and it'll be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Pinion of the Sea of Fog addressing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotion and cooperation are at the essence of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By joining the Kugel fleet, the Flange fleet will attain even greater prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you to make the wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing but a well-phrased demand to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet we have no choice but to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it you are the leader of this fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to resolve this peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to tear our fleet apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships will be selected according to their ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fleet is like our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Only together does it function.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you are to contribute to an even greater family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness shall come to those who follow Providence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the judgment of God shall fall upon those who oppose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kneel. We shall grant you the Blessing.{Xythar, consider a comma after this "Then."}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,May you devote your life and ability to work in the name of Providence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks pretty different from the other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys must be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no money here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you live without money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,People receive rations based on their contributions to the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very fair community.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your living quarters are this way. I'll show you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ships are splitting up and joining the fleet as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Splitting up"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course. Did you expect us to be so naive as to keep potential insurgents in one place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask us to join then you treat us like insurgents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, it would be most wise if you refrained from contacting your friends for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Virus data analysis complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing medical examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical examination complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No abnormalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colonel commanded a fleet from such cramped a spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't measure up to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I conjecture that Colonel Kugel's withdrawal to his cockpit had the effect 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of turning his figure into a symbol and provoke sentiments of awe among fleet members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears to have led to his current strong authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You fear what you can't see, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But is keeping these people perpetually afraid the right path?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is the most primal animal reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,While those who oppose him see fear as the root of his authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it nevertheless provides peace and safety to those who obey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been concluded that rule through force is effective in the fight against the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It enables the mobilization of a large number of personnel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the maintenance of a stable and responsive community.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... I shouldn't have left the cockpit either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the man called Pinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we dispose of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His skills are genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, idling around all day has gotten boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Waking process complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmission from Colonel Kugel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in need of your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the Hideauze, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's missionary work among the folk of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As you command, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're here and we've got two Machine Calibers at our disposal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can proceed with the large-scale missionary work I've been planning for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
